# Design System — Vibrant Logistics (PWA)

> Source of truth: `design.md` in the repo root.  
> Tokens are mapped to CSS variables (shadcn pattern) and Tailwind utilities below.

---

## Colors

### Primary — Purple `#451ebb`
| Use | Tailwind class |
|---|---|
| Primary button bg | `bg-primary` |
| Primary button text | `text-primary-foreground` |
| Primary container (darker) | `bg-primary-container` |
| Highlight / accent bg | `bg-accent` |
| Accent text | `text-accent-foreground` |
| Focus ring | automatic via `ring` CSS var |

### Surface Elevation (Tonal Layers — no shadows)
| Level | Tailwind class | Hex | When to use |
|---|---|---|---|
| Lowest (cards) | `bg-surface-lowest` or `bg-card` | `#ffffff` | Cards, list items |
| Low | `bg-surface-low` | `#f3f3f6` | Section backgrounds |
| Default | `bg-surface` or `bg-muted` | `#eeeef0` | Container fills |
| High | `bg-surface-high` | `#e8e8ea` | Selected / active row |
| Highest | `bg-surface-highest` | `#e2e2e5` | Pressed state |
| Background | `bg-background` | `#f9f9fc` | Page canvas |

### Semantic
| Token | Tailwind class | Hex | Use |
|---|---|---|---|
| Text (primary) | `text-foreground` | `#1a1c1e` | All body text |
| Text (secondary) | `text-muted-foreground` | `#484554` | Labels, hints |
| Border | `border-border` | `#c9c4d7` | Cards, inputs, dividers |
| Outline | `text-outline` | `#797586` | Icon-only borders |
| Tertiary / Amber | `bg-tertiary-container` + `text-tertiary-foreground` | Amber | Warnings, priority |
| Error | `bg-destructive` + `text-destructive-foreground` | `#ba1a1a` | Error states |

