## Typography

| Style | Tailwind class | Font | Use |
|---|---|---|---|
| Page title | `text-headline-lg font-bold font-sans` | Plus Jakarta Sans 24/700 | Screen headers |
| Section title | `text-headline-md font-semibold font-sans` | Plus Jakarta Sans 20/600 | Card/section headers |
| Body default | `text-body-lg font-sans` | Plus Jakarta Sans 16/400 | Descriptions |
| Body small | `text-body-md font-sans` | Plus Jakarta Sans 14/400 | Secondary text |
| Label (tag, caption) | `text-label-md font-label` | Inter 12/500 | Status chips, timestamps |
| Label tiny (SKU, code) | `text-label-sm font-label uppercase tracking-wider` | Inter 10/600 | Barcodes, SKUs |

```tsx
// ✅ Page header
<h1 className="text-headline-lg font-bold text-foreground">Recebimento</h1>

// ✅ Status label (Inter)
<span className="text-label-md font-label text-muted-foreground">Cod: 00123</span>
```

