## Spacing

| Token | Value | Tailwind |
|---|---|---|
| xs | 4px | `p-xs` / `gap-xs` |
| sm | 8px | `p-sm` / `gap-sm` |
| md | 16px | `p-md` / `gap-md` — default card padding |
| lg | 24px | `p-lg` / `gap-lg` |
| xl | 32px | `p-xl` / `gap-xl` |
| gutter | 12px | `gap-gutter` — vertical list stacks |
| margin-mobile | 20px | `px-margin-mobile` — horizontal safe edges |

