## Border Radius

| Token | Value | Use |
|---|---|---|
| `rounded` (default) | 8px | Inputs, small containers |
| `rounded-lg` | 16px | **Cards, primary buttons** |
| `rounded-full` | 9999px | Status chips / pills |

