## Components

### Button
```tsx
// Primary
<button className="min-h-btn rounded-lg bg-primary text-primary-foreground px-md font-semibold active:scale-95 transition-transform">
  Confirmar
</button>

// Secondary (outline)
<button className="min-h-btn rounded-lg border border-primary text-primary bg-transparent px-md font-semibold">
  Cancelar
</button>
```

### Card (warehouse task item)
```tsx
<div className="bg-card rounded-lg border border-border p-md shadow-sm">
  {/* quantity / location bold, top-right */}
</div>
```

### Status Chip
```tsx
// Use rounded-full + low-sat bg + high-sat text
<span className="rounded-full px-sm py-0.5 text-label-md font-label bg-tertiary-container text-tertiary">
  Urgente
</span>
```

### Input
```tsx
// Subtle border → turns primary on focus (shadcn Input handles this)
<Input className="rounded border-border focus:border-primary focus:ring-primary" />
```

